Tyree Teko SMITH, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 13-10304. Supreme Court of the United States June 30, 2014. Case below, 556 Fed.Appx. 178 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied. Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
